				<DIV></DIV>
<P>If you would like to be highlighted on EQPlayers, take the questionnaire below, fill it out in Word or notepad&nbsp;and send it to me by email to <A href="mailto:cdelzer@soe.sony.com" target=_blank>cdelzer@soe.sony.com</A> with "Weekly Player Highlight" as the subject.&nbsp; Include if you wish, a real life picture and a screenshot of your primary character.&nbsp; Highlights will generally be done once a week in the order they are received so do not be surprised if your highlight is not done the same week you submit it.</P>
<P>*********************</P>
<P>Real life first name:<BR>Main Character name:<BR>Server:<BR>Guild:</P>
<P><BR>Where in the real life world do you live? (city &amp; state or equivalent only please!) </P>
<P>How long have you played EQ??<BR>&nbsp;<BR>What other MMOs have you played?<BR>&nbsp;<BR>What type of work do you do?<BR>&nbsp;<BR>How long is your typical gaming session when playing EQ?<BR>&nbsp;<BR>What does a typical EQ day consist of for you?</P>
<P>What was the race and class of your very first character?</P>
<P>What got you into gaming and what sort of games do you like the most?<BR>&nbsp;<BR>What other hobbies or activities do you take part in, other then playing EverQuest? </P>
<P>What is your highest level in EQ?<BR>&nbsp;<BR>What race and class is your main character?</P>
<P>What do you like the most about the class you have chosen for your main character?</P>
<P>Does your main character worship a deity?<BR>&nbsp;<BR>How did you choose your main character's name?</P>
<P>Which classes in EQ have you NOT played?</P>
<P>What is your favorite expansion?</P>
<P>What is your favorite zone?</P>
<P>What is your favorite npc?</P>
<P>Which expansion do you like the least?</P>
<P>Which zone do you like the least?</P>
<P>Which npc do you like the least?</P>
<P>What is the most platinum you have ever spent on purchasing a single item for one of your characters?</P>
<P>Do you have an item you no longer use but keep around for nostalgic reasons?&nbsp; If so what is it and why do you keep it?</P>
<P>What do you like best about EverQuest?</P>
<P>What do you get out of playing EverQuest?</P>
<P>Describe your best experience from playing EverQuest?</P>
<P>Do you run or work for an EverQuest Fan Site?&nbsp; (if so provide the web address too!)</P>
				
